SOLID:

S - Single-responsibility Principle

Wrong:
$shapes = [
  new Circle(2),
  new Square(5),
  new Square(6),
];

$areas = new AreaCalculator($shapes); // gives JSON
echo $areas->output();

Correct:
$shapes = [
  new Circle(2),
  new Square(5),
  new Square(6),
];

$areas = new AreaCalculator($shapes); // Gives Number
$output = new SumCalculatorOutputter($areas);

echo $output->JSON();
echo $output->HTML();


